name: Cases not provided for in chapter
text: §556-10  Cases not provided for in chapter.  In any case not provided for in this chapter the rules of law and equity, including the law merchant and those rules of law and equity relating to trusts, agency, negotiable instruments, and banking, shall continue to apply. [L 1945, c 197, §12; RL 1955, §189-11; HRS §556-10]
